{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-offer-technical-support-and-guidance/task-18","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-offer-technical-support-and-guidance","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovom razgovoru Sarah objašnjava važne koncepte u programiranju. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Encounter</span> znači susresti se sa nečim, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">potential issues</span> su mogući problemi, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">conditional statements</span> su delovi koda koji se izvršavaju samo ako su određeni uslovi ispunjeni, a <span class=\"highlighted-text\">gracefully</span> znači rešavati probleme na miran i kontrolisan način.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-offer-technical-support-and-guidance/task-18"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta Sarah savetuje Tomu u vezi sa upravljanjem greškama u programu?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Korišćenje uslovnih izraza za mirno upravljanje mogućim problemima.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kupuuza matatizo yoyote yanayoweza kutokea</p>","feedback":"<p>Ignorisanje problema koji mogu nastati nije dobra navika. Sara savetuje da se njima upravlja smireno.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Zaustavite program čim se pojave greške</p>","feedback":"<p>Zaustavljanje programa nije mirno upravljanje greškama. Sarah govori o njihovom kontrolisanom rešavanju.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Fokusirati se samo na greške koje se često pojavljuju.</p>","feedback":"<p>Fokusiranje samo na česte greške ne pokriva sve moguće probleme. Sarah govori o mirnom upravljanju svim mogućim problemima.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":1}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room3.png","characters":[{"character":"Sarah","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"9.1-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":27.42,"finishTimestamp":34.98},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":4.88,"dialogue":{"text":"Now, let's talk about error handling. If you encounter potential issues,","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.22,"finishTime":8.56,"dialogue":{"text":"it's a good idea to use conditional statements to handle them gracefully.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sarah","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":9.06,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 18","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-offer-technical-support-and-guidance","dashedName":"task-18","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-offer-technical-support-and-guidance","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-offer-technical-support-and-guidance/task-19","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-offer-technical-support-and-guidance/task-17","id":"6620d6cd9452910c27da19f1","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-offer-technical-support-and-guidance/task-18"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520